divs: sighting detailssitting on deck at home and noticed in eastern sky, a little distance above the treeline, five (5)solid green orbs, no other colors or flashing lights, evenly spaced apart and moving in a straight line slowly from the south to the north...no sound. the apparent distance and speed appeared same as the pattern of a typical jet. however, jets generally fly east-west or west-east, as well as marking\flashing lights. the sighting was observed, from south to north, approximately 15 minutes and out of our view.
Summary: Observed 5 solid green orbs, no other colors or flashing lights, evenly spaced apart moving in straight line slowly from the south to the north...no sound. Distance away and speed appeared same as pattern of a typical jet.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Ankeny
There were no other sightings in Ankeny on or around July 4th 2012
